1
00:00:06,740 --> 00:00:11,177
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

2
00:00:11,244 --> 00:00:14,771
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

3
00:00:14,848 --> 00:00:18,284
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

4
00:00:18,351 --> 00:00:21,946
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way</i>

5
00:00:22,022 --> 00:00:25,287
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

6
00:00:25,358 --> 00:00:27,292
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,095 --> 00:00:32,030
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,098 --> 00:00:35,898
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,303 --> 00:00:43,141
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,376 --> 00:00:50,441
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:56,882
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,023 --> 00:01:01,289
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,361 --> 00:01:04,956
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,031 --> 00:01:08,364
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,435 --> 00:01:12,064
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,138 --> 00:01:15,733
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:15,809 --> 00:01:19,301
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,379 --> 00:01:22,974
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,049 --> 00:01:27,145
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:02:06,737 --> 00:02:12,676
<i>A Dubious Offer!</i>
<i>Tsunade's Choice</i>

21
00:02:18,215 --> 00:02:19,113
Not good...

22
00:02:21,018 --> 00:02:26,422
Dang it! Dang it!
This time for sure... no matter what!

23
00:02:38,669 --> 00:02:42,503
<i>You're the only one who can treat</i>
<i>Lord Orochimaru's arms.</i>

24
00:02:45,142 --> 00:02:46,769
<i>Why don't we make a deal?</i>

25
00:02:49,914 --> 00:02:55,147
<i>I'll resurrect the little brother</i>
<i>and man, both of whom you loved...</i>

26
00:02:55,886 --> 00:02:59,049
<i>with the Forbidden Jutsu I've developed.</i>

27
00:03:00,257 --> 00:03:03,454
<i>Don't you want to see those two,</i>
<i>Tsunade...?</i>

28
00:03:04,128 --> 00:03:06,995
<i>No! You must not believe</i>
<i>in their sweet talk...</i>

29
00:03:08,365 --> 00:03:11,425
<i>Their wishes...</i>
<i>Moreover, Tsunade, your wishes...</i>

30
00:03:11,502 --> 00:03:13,299
<i>And dreams...</i>
<i>Did you forget them?!</i>

31
00:03:14,138 --> 00:03:15,662
<i>I'll be straight with you.</i>

32
00:03:16,006 --> 00:03:21,967
<i>Tsunade, the village has demanded</i>
<i>that you become the Fifth Hokage.</i>

33
00:03:23,147 --> 00:03:24,876
<i>The successive line of Hokages</i>

34
00:03:24,949 --> 00:03:27,747
<i>have protected the Leaf Village</i>
<i>and those living in it.</i>

35
00:03:27,818 --> 00:03:29,410
<i>They brought troubled times under control</i>

36
00:03:29,486 --> 00:03:32,011
<i>and helped the village to prosper.</i>

37
00:03:32,089 --> 00:03:34,284
<i>They risked their lives for</i>
<i>this dream, this ideal!</i>

38
00:03:37,494 --> 00:03:39,928
<i>You don't have to answer right now.</i>

39
00:03:41,565 --> 00:03:44,728
<i>However, I want it in a week.</i>

40
00:03:45,836 --> 00:03:49,397
<i>Also, two human sacrifices are</i>
<i>needed for this Forbidden Jutsu,</i>

41
00:03:50,741 --> 00:03:53,710
<i>so do what you need to do</i>
<i>to prepare them.</i>

42
00:04:05,956 --> 00:04:07,184
We are starting!

43
00:04:11,695 --> 00:04:13,595
C'mon. Place your bets!

44
00:04:16,634 --> 00:04:19,034
Which will you bet on, ma'am?

45
00:04:21,005 --> 00:04:22,870
Which one? C'mon!

46
00:04:24,708 --> 00:04:26,141
Which one will she choose?

47
00:04:27,444 --> 00:04:30,811
If she agrees to our conditions,

48
00:04:31,415 --> 00:04:33,349
your arms will be healed,

49
00:04:33,417 --> 00:04:35,908
and the destruction of the Leaf Village
will continue immediately.

50
00:04:37,187 --> 00:04:40,247
Lady Tsunade will also be able to
be reunited with the two whom she loves.

51
00:04:42,493 --> 00:04:45,758
But if she doesn't agree...

52
00:04:46,030 --> 00:04:50,057
I'll have to force her to heal my arms...

53
00:04:52,336 --> 00:04:54,167
Will it really be that easy?

54
00:04:54,672 --> 00:04:56,071
I have you.

55
00:05:00,344 --> 00:05:01,811
There's no need to worry.

56
00:05:02,513 --> 00:05:06,176
I'm the one who knows her the best.

57
00:05:07,518 --> 00:05:09,782
And her greatest weakness!

58
00:05:11,121 --> 00:05:16,252
She'll definitely accept the conditions...
Definitely!

59
00:05:26,470 --> 00:05:29,132
<i>Listen, in this third step,</i>

60
00:05:29,206 --> 00:05:32,073
<i>you've got to use 100%</i>
<i>of what you have learned...</i>

61
00:05:32,142 --> 00:05:33,473
<i>And retain them.</i>

62
00:05:46,490 --> 00:05:47,548
<i>In other words,</i>

63
00:05:47,624 --> 00:05:50,354
<i>imagine creating a single layer</i>
<i>within the balloon</i>

64
00:05:50,427 --> 00:05:53,328
<i>and compressing the Chakra inside it.</i>

65
00:05:55,232 --> 00:05:58,463
<i>I know that in my head...</i>

66
00:05:59,169 --> 00:06:00,727
<i>But no matter what,</i>

67
00:06:01,071 --> 00:06:05,132
<i>I can't completely hold 100%</i>
<i>of my power in a neat ball...</i>

68
00:06:27,197 --> 00:06:31,497
<i>Don't give him false hope by teaching him</i>
<i>something he can't master.</i>

69
00:06:32,536 --> 00:06:38,338
<i>That's why the moony kid</i>
<i>starts joking about becoming a Hokage!</i>

70
00:06:52,990 --> 00:06:53,957
Tomorrow, huh.

71
00:06:58,295 --> 00:06:59,660
Come again, okay?

72
00:07:00,664 --> 00:07:02,097
I certainly will!

73
00:07:17,681 --> 00:07:19,774
<i>Are you going to meet</i>
<i>Orochimaru again?</i>

74
00:07:27,691 --> 00:07:30,285
<i>To think she'd be that shaken up...</i>

75
00:07:31,128 --> 00:07:33,289
<i>Something extreme must have happened.</i>

76
00:07:35,165 --> 00:07:38,532
<i>That one week bugs me, somehow...</i>

77
00:07:44,708 --> 00:07:48,701
<i>And Naruto hasn't come back</i>
<i>to the inn for nearly a week.</i>

78
00:07:50,013 --> 00:07:53,380
<i>I guess I'll press Tsunade a little more.</i>

79
00:08:06,563 --> 00:08:07,587
<i>No good...</i>

80
00:08:11,268 --> 00:08:12,826
<i>No good... Why?</i>

81
00:08:14,538 --> 00:08:19,032
<i>Here there's no time...</i>
<i>It'll be too late.</i>

82
00:08:27,618 --> 00:08:28,550
What's this...?!

83
00:08:32,022 --> 00:08:33,819
What happened, Naruto?!

84
00:08:34,291 --> 00:08:35,258
Are you okay?

85
00:08:51,542 --> 00:08:52,531
What do you want?

86
00:08:53,677 --> 00:08:55,042
The moon's out.

87
00:08:57,414 --> 00:08:58,847
How about going out for a drink?

88
00:09:08,892 --> 00:09:12,760
Tomorrow will be the one week
you promised to Naruto.

89
00:09:19,469 --> 00:09:22,199
I wonder what became of Naruto?

90
00:09:25,576 --> 00:09:26,668
Beats me.

91
00:09:32,983 --> 00:09:34,416
I guess I'll have something.

92
00:09:34,685 --> 00:09:35,743
Radish, please.

93
00:09:35,953 --> 00:09:36,817
Coming up.

94
00:09:49,066 --> 00:09:50,260
Oh?

95
00:09:55,372 --> 00:09:56,339
Here you go.

96
00:09:57,541 --> 00:10:00,339
Ooh! This looks good.

97
00:10:22,966 --> 00:10:23,955
Lady Tsunade!

98
00:10:26,770 --> 00:10:27,862
What happened to Naruto?

99
00:10:29,273 --> 00:10:30,740
He's quite exhausted and weakened.

100
00:10:32,576 --> 00:10:34,737
And his right hand is severely burned
with Chakra...

101
00:10:36,780 --> 00:10:38,543
As it stands now,

102
00:10:38,915 --> 00:10:40,940
this kid probably won't wake up
until the day after tomorrow.

103
00:10:44,388 --> 00:10:45,912
It's as Jiraiya says...

104
00:10:47,457 --> 00:10:50,051
Why did I make such a stupid bet?

105
00:10:52,029 --> 00:10:55,123
What am I, of all people,
getting so worked up for?

106
00:10:56,133 --> 00:10:57,430
How stupid.

107
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:03,938
Tomorrow...

108
00:11:06,743 --> 00:11:08,540
Please don't go tomorrow!

109
00:11:12,616 --> 00:11:14,982
Why don't you say anything?!

110
00:11:15,452 --> 00:11:18,512
Lady Tsunade! Please don't be silent.
Please answer!

111
00:11:21,391 --> 00:11:23,018
If you say that you're going...

112
00:11:24,961 --> 00:11:26,121
What will you do?

113
00:11:26,897 --> 00:11:29,559
I'll stop you with my life!

114
00:11:33,470 --> 00:11:37,031
Shizune... Have you forgotten
who you're talking to?

115
00:12:00,530 --> 00:12:04,694
Sir! It's morning, now!
It's about time you went home!

116
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:07,534
Geez.

117
00:12:11,408 --> 00:12:14,536
Hey! Get up, sir...

118
00:12:19,783 --> 00:12:21,944
Hey! What's wrong, you?!

119
00:12:30,995 --> 00:12:34,192
It'll be troublesome if we're disturbed
during the negotiations...

120
00:12:35,366 --> 00:12:36,264
What do you want me to do?

121
00:12:37,435 --> 00:12:42,304
It might be good to kill...
Tsunade's attendant.

122
00:12:48,713 --> 00:12:50,146
<i>It seems that you...</i>

123
00:12:50,415 --> 00:12:53,077
<i>You don't trust me completely...yet.</i>

124
00:12:54,786 --> 00:12:57,050
<i>Precisely because I trust you...</i>

125
00:12:59,257 --> 00:13:02,090
<i>I would like to leave Sasuke</i>
<i>in your hands.</i>

126
00:13:05,029 --> 00:13:05,996
<i>Well, then...</i>

127
00:13:06,597 --> 00:13:08,565
<i>Kabuto...</i>

128
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:11,498
<i>If you wish to stop me...</i>

129
00:13:12,303 --> 00:13:16,364
<i>You have no choice</i>
<i>but to kill young Sasuke, now.</i>

130
00:13:17,775 --> 00:13:20,869
<i>You can't possibly kill me...</i>

131
00:13:27,518 --> 00:13:28,212
Hey!

132
00:13:29,387 --> 00:13:30,752
I said hey!

133
00:13:34,959 --> 00:13:36,153
Naruto?

134
00:13:37,895 --> 00:13:42,696
Oh no! What time is it?
No, what day is it?

135
00:13:43,701 --> 00:13:44,929
It's Monday...

136
00:13:47,805 --> 00:13:49,238
What is it?

137
00:13:50,108 --> 00:13:52,474
Is your body okay?

138
00:13:53,444 --> 00:13:56,345
As I recall, you were supposed
to sleep for two full days...

139
00:13:57,849 --> 00:13:59,009
No matter what the wound,

140
00:13:59,083 --> 00:14:04,817
I'm always able to recover
if I sleep one night!

141
00:14:05,757 --> 00:14:08,419
<i>That's right.</i>
<i>This kid has Nine Tailed Fox's power...</i>

142
00:14:09,026 --> 00:14:12,484
More importantly,
where's that stupid old woman?!

143
00:14:12,997 --> 00:14:15,898
Today's the promised bet day.

144
00:14:15,967 --> 00:14:17,696
Then, what about the Jutsu...

145
00:14:19,937 --> 00:14:24,135
It's still not complete, but I can wing it...
Believe it!

146
00:14:28,246 --> 00:14:30,214
<i>That's right. This isn't the time for this.</i>

147
00:14:30,882 --> 00:14:32,816
- Naruto, please stay...
- Huh?

148
00:14:35,453 --> 00:14:36,420
You are...!

149
00:14:37,221 --> 00:14:38,813
What?! Oh!

150
00:14:44,195 --> 00:14:45,856
Wait, Shizune!

151
00:14:48,533 --> 00:14:53,368
That darned Tsunade spiked my drink.

152
00:14:54,305 --> 00:14:56,865
I can't build up my Chakra well...

153
00:14:57,074 --> 00:15:01,170
And my body is so numb,
I can barely throw a Kunai Knife.

154
00:15:02,647 --> 00:15:05,343
<i>What was he gonna do</i>
<i>if that had hit me?!</i>

155
00:15:05,850 --> 00:15:10,219
That's lame! Here you're always bragging
about how you're this awesome Ninja!

156
00:15:10,288 --> 00:15:13,086
And you're nailed by her perverted attack?
You, Pervy Pervy Sage?!

157
00:15:13,157 --> 00:15:14,454
Shut up!

158
00:15:16,027 --> 00:15:19,053
Even if she's rotten,
she's still a medical specialist.

159
00:15:20,031 --> 00:15:25,663
She's the only one who could concoct
a tasteless and odorless drug for Ninja.

160
00:15:27,071 --> 00:15:30,802
But to think I'd be caught off-guard,

161
00:15:30,875 --> 00:15:32,536
no matter how intoxicated I was...

162
00:15:48,860 --> 00:15:50,919
<i>I'm going to kill you, bastard!</i>

163
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:04,699
How are you feeling,
Master Jiraiya?

164
00:16:05,810 --> 00:16:08,870
Quite a bit better than this morning I guess.

165
00:16:09,413 --> 00:16:11,711
But be that as it may,
maybe around thirty percent...

166
00:16:15,653 --> 00:16:19,248
<i>I never thought I'd end up encountering</i>
<i>that Master Jiraiya in a place like this...</i>

167
00:16:20,625 --> 00:16:24,686
<i>Things have gotten difficult.</i>
<i>I guess I'll pull back for now.</i>

168
00:16:26,531 --> 00:16:30,991
<i>At any rate, Naruto...</i>
<i>To think you'd be here, too...</i>

169
00:16:40,344 --> 00:16:41,606
Hey! Shizune.

170
00:16:41,679 --> 00:16:43,112
Y-Yes?!

171
00:16:43,915 --> 00:16:45,348
It's about time you tell me

172
00:16:45,416 --> 00:16:49,716
what the heck she was talking about
with Orochimaru.

173
00:16:50,521 --> 00:16:51,579
Orochimaru?!

174
00:16:56,827 --> 00:16:59,091
I wanted to believe Lady Tsunade...

175
00:17:00,598 --> 00:17:03,396
That's why I couldn't say until now.

176
00:17:05,269 --> 00:17:06,065
But...

177
00:17:08,673 --> 00:17:11,699
There's no time.
Please come with me!

178
00:17:12,276 --> 00:17:13,675
I'll explain as we run!

179
00:17:13,844 --> 00:17:14,640
Okay!

180
00:17:14,712 --> 00:17:16,043
I'm going, too!

181
00:17:37,802 --> 00:17:38,894
What's your answer?

182
00:17:40,938 --> 00:17:42,235
Say what?!

183
00:17:43,874 --> 00:17:46,172
The answer to that is definitely no!

184
00:17:47,111 --> 00:17:50,239
<i>This might be really bad...</i>

185
00:17:51,449 --> 00:17:56,079
<i>She's probably still thinking</i>
<i>of those two.</i>

186
00:17:59,991 --> 00:18:04,690
<i>Perhaps I may have no choice,</i>
<i>but to kill Tsunade...</i>

187
00:18:06,564 --> 00:18:08,156
<i>Dang it!</i>

188
00:18:20,511 --> 00:18:21,876
I'll heal your arms...

189
00:18:23,247 --> 00:18:26,216
In exchange for that,
keep your hands off the village.

190
00:18:29,153 --> 00:18:30,415
Very well.

191
00:19:10,394 --> 00:19:11,361
Now then...

192
00:19:27,678 --> 00:19:29,612
He's planning to once again attack

193
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:31,671
the Leaf Village if
his arms are healed!

194
00:19:32,349 --> 00:19:36,149
The situation will get
even more dangerous than that

195
00:19:36,220 --> 00:19:38,211
if he's not stopped now.

196
00:19:38,723 --> 00:19:40,588
Him screwing around like that!

197
00:19:44,795 --> 00:19:48,629
<i>I have you.</i>
<i>There's no need to worry...</i>

198
00:20:50,094 --> 00:20:51,755
What's the meaning of this?

199
00:20:52,863 --> 00:20:55,855
To think you'd betray me at this point...

200
00:21:03,274 --> 00:21:04,298
Tsunade!

201
00:21:05,743 --> 00:21:10,442
<i>I believe your promise,</i>
<i>its a true heart give me courage</i>

202
00:21:10,514 --> 00:21:14,848
<i>Always I feel it</i>
<i>the precious time with you</i>

203
00:21:15,453 --> 00:21:18,980
<i>On your still shoulder</i>

204
00:21:20,224 --> 00:21:24,684
<i>I feel the wind that blows</i>
<i>towards tomorrow</i>

205
00:21:24,862 --> 00:21:30,300
<i>The city lights are like pieces of stars</i>

206
00:21:30,801 --> 00:21:35,101
<i>That hold us together</i>

207
00:21:35,573 --> 00:21:44,811
<i>"Each one of us glows differently,"</i>

208
00:21:44,882 --> 00:21:47,476
<i>you say laughingly</i>

209
00:21:47,718 --> 00:21:53,384
<i>but you look most dazzling</i>

210
00:21:53,958 --> 00:21:58,327
<i>Like a comet,</i>

211
00:21:58,396 --> 00:22:04,494
<i>like the rainbow after the storm</i>

212
00:22:04,568 --> 00:22:11,667
<i>You bring light into my heart</i>

213
00:22:12,677 --> 00:22:22,052
<i>Being lost can be the answer</i>

214
00:22:23,387 --> 00:22:30,919
<i>Let's promise we won't cheat</i>

215
00:22:30,995 --> 00:22:34,988
<i>Uh...like a shooting star,</i>
<i>we do go ahead.</i>

216
00:22:37,735 --> 00:22:41,102
What the hell is this?! This castle
has been destroyed even further!

217
00:22:41,172 --> 00:22:44,801
It seems Tsunade has
declined the deal.

218
00:22:44,875 --> 00:22:47,275
But... but the old lady is not here!

219
00:22:47,344 --> 00:22:50,040
Calm down a second.
She shouldn't have gone far from here.

220
00:22:50,114 --> 00:22:52,844
Oh, some incredible noise
from that direction, Pervy Sage!

221
00:22:52,917 --> 00:22:55,249
Well, well... she started a flashy battle.

222
00:22:55,419 --> 00:22:56,716
Naruto, we go after her!

223
00:22:56,787 --> 00:22:59,381
Right! I'm ready anytime!

224
00:22:59,990 --> 00:23:01,821
Next time:
"Breakdown! The Deal is Off!"
